湖北中部农村防疫日记：买不到口罩，外地归乡人不知道疫情。
Hubei central rural epidemic prevention diary: can not buy masks, people do not know the epidemic situation.
刘亚丹。
Liu Yadan.
清流工作室                      。
Cleaning Studio.
清流工作室。
Cleaning Studio.
穿透迷雾，探寻真相。
Through the fog, seek the truth.
网易财经旗下原创深度报道团队，专注上市公司调查。
Netease Finance's original in-depth reporting team, focused on the listed companies investigation.
。
.
截止到大年初二（1月26日），村里通往外面的路完全封了，只出不进。
By the second day of the New Year (January 26), the road to the outside of the village was completely closed except for the entrance.
村里没有多少口罩，疫情开始严重前，镇上就买不到口罩。
There were not many face masks in the village, and the town could not buy them before the outbreak began to get serious.
直到1月22日，从外地做生意归乡的亲人中，还有人根本不知道这次疫情。
Until January 22, some of those who returned home from business outside the country had no knowledge of the outbreak.
出品|网易清流工作室作者|刘亚丹 主编|赵妍爆料邮箱：stoolpigeon@service.netease.com坐标在湖北省中部的一个村庄，属于鄂中荆门市两县交接地带。
AT & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
2020年1月25日0-24时，荆门市新增新型冠状病毒感染确诊病例17例，共确诊病例38例。
January 25, 2020 0-24 hours, Jingmen City, a new type of coronavirus infection confirmed 17 cases, a total of 38 confirmed cases.
据央视新闻报道，截至2020年1月21日24时，我们县（沙洋县）发现新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疑似病例2例，邻县钟祥1例。
As of 2400 hours on January 21, 2020, two suspected cases of pneumonia with a new coronavirus infection were found in our county, Shayang county, and one case in a neighboring county, Zhongxiang, CCTV reported.
即使身处互联网时代，乡下很多人的信息来源，还是亲友乡邻之间的人际传播。
Even in the age of the Internet, the source of information for many people in the countryside is interpersonal communication between friends and neighbors.
我姑姑一家1月22日（腊月28日）回家，完全没有听说过疫情，村里也有人是返乡半路才被亲友电话通知消息。
My aunt and I returned home on January 22 (28 December). There was no news of the outbreak, and some people in the village were on their way home to be informed by telephone.
我堂哥因为没有疫情认识，开车接了一个从武汉返乡的亲戚，没戴口罩也没做任何防护。
My cousin, unaware of the outbreak, picked up a relative returning from Wuhan without a mask or any protection.
1月25日，（正月初一），市里也封城了，我堂哥才意识到严重性，他很慌张，在微信家族群里问我们怎么办。
January 25 (the first day of the first month), the city also closed, my cousin just realized the seriousness, he was very flustered, in the micro-letter family asked us what to do.
（大年初二，村里的路已封。
The village road was sealed on the second day of the New Year.
图片来自文中疫区村民）（大年初二，村里停止了一切拜年活动，乡亲们站在路上聊天。
On the second day of the Lunar New Year, the village stopped all New Year's Eve activities and villagers stood chatting on the road.
戴口罩的依然不多。
The number of masks is still low.
刘亚丹摄）最开始引起重视的是我们这些从外地回家的年轻人。
The first thing that caught my eye was the young people who came home from other places.
开始我们都是劝说家里人要戴口罩，不要出门，在家族群里，我和我姐不断发布最新的消息。
At first we tried to persuade my family to wear masks and not to go out. In the family, my sister and I kept up-to-date.
1月21日，我早上起床，发现我爸爸没有戴口罩就去集市卖藕，一时非常紧张和生气。
January 21, I got up in the morning, found that my father did not wear a mask to sell lotus root market, very nervous and angry.
那时候网路上传播的也都是“父母一代不戴口罩”的说法。
At that time, the Internet also spread the word "parents do not wear a mask generation."
我爸说，他在镇上集市看到，大概只有十分之一的人戴口罩。
My dad said he saw at the town fair that only about one in ten people wore masks.
镇上也买不到医用口罩，我爸爸就买了几个劳保用的口罩回家，分给了我姑姑一个。
The town could not buy a medical mask, so my father bought a few labor masks and gave them to my aunt.
1月22日，我们县城沙洋和临县钟祥，都有了疑似的病例。
January 22, our county Shayang and adjacent county Zhongxiang, have suspected cases.
但是村里面极少人戴口罩。
But few people in the village wear masks.
尽管我和姐姐在家族群里不停发消息，但还是有表哥们在市区找人开房打麻将。
Although my sister and I kept sending messages through the family, my cousins were still looking for someone to open a house and play Mahjong downtown.
晚上村里的集体散步活动中，我戴着我爸爸买的白色劳保口罩从村头走到村尾好几次，算是自我认为的疫情宣传和普及。
In the evening group walks in the village, I wore my father's white labor mask from the village head to the end of several times, as a self-perceived epidemic propaganda and popularization.
这天，我们村的小卖部门口，也贴出了一张疫情介绍告示。
On this day, our village commissary entrance, also posted an epidemic situation introduction notice.
（村里陆续张贴的疫情通知告示。
Notices of disease have been posted in the village.
刘亚丹摄）想到县城、市区比武汉的医疗系统更加薄弱，乡下乡亲们普遍不重视、不防备，我不断告诉我爸妈，不要再接触外人。
Liu Yadan think of the county, urban areas than Wuhan more weak medical system, rural villagers generally do not pay attention to, do not guard, I repeatedly told my parents, do not contact outsiders.
我姑姑从外地回家之后，我就半开玩笑的表示不愿意和他们接触。
When my aunt came home from the field, I half joked that I did not want to contact them.
一方面，我从武汉回来，还没有过14天的“潜伏期“；另一方面，他们还没有意识到防御措施，随便接触人群。
On the one hand, I returned from Wuhan without a 14-day incubation period. On the other hand, they were not aware of the defensive measures and came into contact with the crowd.
1月23日，武汉封城。
Wuhan Sealed on January 23.
我开始说服我爸，过年不要拜年，也不要让亲友们来家里拜年，成功说服我爸之后，又开始去家族群倡议不要拜年。
I began to convince my father, New Year, do not let friends and relatives to visit the New Year, successfully convinced my father, and then began to family group initiative not to pay a New Year call.
这天晚上，我们村干部戴着口罩到我们家登记外来人口，这时候算是全村都开始重视了。
That night, our village cadres came to our house wearing masks to register the foreign population, by this time the whole village began to pay attention.
我对村干部说：“给我们发口罩吧。
"Give us masks," I told village officials.
”村干部说：“我都没有口罩，怎么给你们发。
"I don't even have a mask," said the village official.
”1月24日（腊月30日）早晨起来，村干部开着车、架着喇叭在村里面传播疫情消息。
On the morning of January 24, village officials drove in cars and honked their horns to spread the word about the outbreak.
我和父母合作，打电话给各方亲友，“今年疫情严重，不拜年了……”。
I work with my parents, call friends and relatives on all sides, "this year's serious epidemic, do not visit the New Year..."
大家都相互理解，村里面过年这几天准备结婚、庆生的喜事基本上也都取消了。
Everyone understands each other, the village in the New Year to prepare for the wedding, the celebration of birthday has also been basically cancelled.
1月25日（正月初一），我们市里已经封城，市里的第一人民医院也发出了医疗物资求助信息，村里的宣传车还是固定早晚宣传。
January 25 (the first day of the first month), our city has been closed down, the city's First People's Hospital also sent out medical supplies help information, the village propaganda car or fixed morning and night propaganda.
这天下雨，气温也很低，早晨起来，村里没有人出门。
It rained and the temperature was low. In the morning no one in the village went out.
往年初一这天都是村里乡亲们相互拜年，今年这天大家都待在家里，闭门不出。
The first day of the New Year is the village folks visit each other, this day we stay at home, the door closed.
下午两点多，我爸妈看电视看到无聊，捂着被子睡到了下午5点。
After 2 pm, my parents watched TV and saw boredom, covering the quilt until 5pm.
晚上，我们收到通知，村里面的路就要被封了，只出不进。
In the evening, we were told that the roads in the village would be sealed off and would not enter.
这时候我妈妈给我小姨舅舅们继续打电话，说明正月初二回外婆家的拜年也都要取消。
At this time my mother to my aunts and uncles continued to call to explain that the second lunar month back to my grandmother's New Year call will also be cancelled.
电话里，我们听到邻镇的小姨们还在走亲戚，聚众打牌。
On the phone, we heard young aunts from neighbouring towns still visiting relatives and getting together to play cards.
仅仅是隔壁镇，不知道她们什么情况。
It's just the next town. I don't know what happened to them.
1月26日（大年初二），雨停了，村里乡亲们昨天都待在家里无聊，开始二、三聚集在村口聊天。
January 26 (New Year's Day), the rain stopped, the villagers stay at home yesterday boring, began to gather at the village mouth to chat.
这天村里通往外面的路已经封了，临乡有了疑似得新冠型肺炎的案例。
The road to the outside of the village had been closed and there was a suspected case of new coronary pneumonia in the countryside.
村里面出来聊天的人，也有人戴口罩，大部分也是没有戴。
Some of the people who came out to chat in the village also wore masks, most of them without wearing them.
“无聊”成了微信上亲友们最大的情绪，于此同时，我发现家里的水果也要告罄了，地里面的蔬菜倒是够吃。
"Boredom" became the biggest emotion among friends and relatives on the line, while I found out that my house was running out of fruit and there was enough vegetables on the floor.
疫情严重前，我们家临时采购了米和煤气。
Before the outbreak, our family bought rice and gas on a temporary basis.
（村里的村干部在张贴村中封路消息。
Village officials are posting up news of the road in the village.
刘亚丹摄）（封村告示，只出不进，村里与邻村的交界路段已经封闭。
(Photo by Liu Yadan) (Notices in the village show that the junction between the village and the neighbouring village has been closed.
刘亚丹摄）村中疫情观察时间表：1月21日，荆门市发现疑似病例。
Photo by Liu Yadan: Suspected cases were found in Jingmen on January 21.
爸爸没有戴口罩就出门去集市卖藕，我很担心。
Dad did not wear a mask to go out to market lotus root, I was very worried.
爸爸回来说，镇上戴口罩的不到十分之一，医用口罩和N95口罩都买不到。
Dad came back and said less than a tenth of the townspeople wore masks. Neither a medical mask nor a N95 mask could be bought.
1月22日，县里已有疑似病例。
On 22 January, there were suspected cases in the district.
姑姑们返乡回家，她们还不知道疫情。
The aunts returned home, and they did not know about the outbreak.
这天晚上村里贴出了第一张疫情告示。
The first outbreak notice was posted in the village that evening.
1月23日。
January 23.
村干部开始登记村里的外来人口。
Village officials began to register the foreign population of the village.
我对村干部说：“给我们发口罩吧。
"Give us masks," I told village officials.
”村干部说：“我都没有口罩，怎么给你们发。
"I don't even have a mask," said the village official.
”1月24日。
"January 24.
村里早晚开始有疫情宣传车播放广播。
Early in the morning, the village began broadcasting epidemic propaganda vehicles.
1月25日。
January 25.
正月初一，村里无人串门拜年，大家都闭门不出。
On the first day of the first month, no one visited the village.
电话得知，临镇的小姨家还在老家聚众打牌。
Telephone learned that the town's auntie family is still in the home crowd playing cards.
1月26日。
January 26.
村里封村，通往邻村的路段全部封闭，只出不进。
The village was sealed off and all the roads leading to the neighbouring village were closed except for access.
村里面出来聊天的人，也有人戴口罩，大部分也是没有戴。
Some of the people who came out to chat in the village also wore masks, most of them without wearing them.
刘亚丹是清流工作室高级作者，常驻广州。
Liu Yadan is the senior author of Qingliu Studio, based in Guangzhou.
